@node "TO-DO" "TODO List for UserEditor"

                        @{b}@{u}TO-DO List for UserEditor@{uu}@{ub}

Well V1.30 is now nearly complete, the only thing missing is the complete
support to edit online users, and this will be implemented for @{b}FAME V2.x@{ub},
as this new Version has now the FAME ToolPort integrated which allows
online editing in a very comfortable way. So please be patient and wait
until the new FAME Release is available, then an Update of UserEditor will
follow with the complete online editing integrated.

@{u}Known Bugs in V1.30:@{uu}

 - none.

@endnode
